      "text": "Peemiant arri tawu Rad-\nditajn tawā Jauntbā / pirms\ntahs taunas Deenas nahk/ un\ntee Gaddi ateet/ no ka tu fazziti:\nTee inan ne pattik.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pirms ta Saule / un tas\nBatschums/ un tas Mehnes/ un\ntahs Swaigsnes tohp aptumscho-\ntas/ un tahs Padebbefis atgree-\nschahs pehz to Leetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tai Deena/ kad ta Nam-\nna Sargi tribfehs/ un tee stipri\nWihti paschi lohzifees / un tee\nMalteneeki kluffu stahwehs / ta-\npelz ka winnu mas irr palikku-\nchi/ un tee/ kas zaur Lohgeim\nkattahs/ taps aptumschoti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tahs diwi Durwis prett\ntelu taps atisslehgtas / ta ka ta\nMalschanas Skunna pawahja\nohp/ un wiꞥsch zettahs ta Put-\nna Balfi dsirdeht / un wiꞥsch\nOseetinn Meitas lohkahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad arri tee preeksch aug-\ntahm Weetahin bihstahs/ un\nailofees pahr to Zeltu/ un tas\nMandekn-Rohks seedehs/ un tas\nSiffenis jew pascham par Nastu\nuhs/ un ta Lihgsmiba aisees/\no tas Zilweks eet uhs to Nam-\nnu fawas Mahschibas / un tee\nSchehtotaji ees us-Eelahm ap-\nahrt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pirms ta Sudraba Wir-\nwe tohp taraustita/ un tas Sel-\nta Awots nistek/ un tas Traufs\npee tahs Akkas iskalst / un tas\nSkrittels pee Akkas falauschahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo teem Pihschleem buhs\natkak Senmē greestees/ itt ka tee\nirr bijuschi/ un tam Garram at-\nkat pee Deewa jagreeschahs/ kas\nto dewis irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tihra Nekeetiba irr / fakka\ntas Mahzitajs : Wisē irr ne-\nleetis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas nu wehl atleek/ tapehz\nka fchis Mahzitajs gudrs btja/\ntad mahzija winsh tohs Laudis\nSinnatchann / un pahrbandija/\nun iswinizaja/ un pataifija dauds\nfakkanus Wahrdus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Mahzitajs mekleja\nfsaiftus Wahrdus atrast/ un ap-\nrakstija pareist pateefus Wahr-\ndus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "To Gudru Wahrdi irr ka\ntee Dsennuti/ un ka Nagglī ee-\nfisti no tahs Draudsibas Mahzi-\ntajeein/ kas no weena Gauna\ndolhti irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas wehl pahr teem at-\nleek : Sargajs/ mans Dehls/\ndauds Grahnatu Darrischanas\nne irr Gals/ un dauds LaAischa-\nnas peekaufe to Meetu.\n"
