      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No wisfa/ kas dsirdehts\nirr/ irr fchis tas Galla Wahrdē:\nBihstees Deewu/ un turri win-\nra Baufius/ jo tas peenahkahs\nwifteem Zilivekcem.\n"
